<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>FitCoachAI — Bêta</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #07070d;
    --bg-2: #0e0e1a;
    --card: #13131f;
    --card-2: #181826;
    --accent: #6c63ff;
    --accent-light: #8b85ff;
    --green: #00d4a4;
    --orange: #ff7a3d;
    --red: #ff4d6d;
    --text: #f4f3fb;
    --text-dim: #9d9bb5;
    --border: #232336;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; }

  html, body {
    background: var(--bg);
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  body {
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  /* ---------- AUTO-SCROLL VIEWPORT ---------- */
  .viewport {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100vh;
    height: 100dvh; /* hauteur réelle visible sur Safari iOS, barre d'adresse repliée ou non */
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .reel {
    width: 100%;
    will-change: transform;
  }

  .glow {
    position: fixed;
    width: 700px; height: 700px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(108,99,255,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .glow-1 { top: -200px; left: -200px; }
  .glow-2 { top: 1400px; right: -250px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,212,164,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%); }
  .glow-3 { top: 3200px; left: -200px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,122,61,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%); }
  .glow-4 { top: 5400px; right: -200px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(108,99,255,0.22) 0%, transparent 70%); }

  section {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 90px 28px;
  }

  /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 60px;
    padding-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 9px 18px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,99,255,0.18), rgba(0,212,164,0.12));
    border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,0.4);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-light);
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .badge .dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--green);
  }

  .hero-icon {
    width: 92px; height: 92px;
    border-radius: 26px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--green));
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 44px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(108,99,255,0.45);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.04;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    max-width: 680px;
  }
  h1 .accent { color: var(--accent-light); }
  h1 .accent-green { color: var(--green); }

  .hero-sub {
    margin-top: 26px;
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 460px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .cta-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 44px;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
    color: white;
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgba(108,99,255,0.5);
  }
  .cta-arrow { font-size: 22px; }

  .cta-note {
    margin-top: 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .cta-note .green-text { color: var(--green); }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 36px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .scroll-hint .chevron {
    font-size: 18px;
    animation: bounce 1.6s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { transform: translateY(8px); opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* ---------- SECTION HEADERS ---------- */
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent-light);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.12;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section-desc {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 480px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ---------- PROBLEM ---------- */
  .problem {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .problem-grid {
    margin-top: 48px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
  }
  .problem-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .problem-card .x {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--red);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .problem-card p {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* ---------- FEATURE BLOCKS ---------- */
  .feature {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .feature-icon-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .feature-icon {
    width: 64px; height: 64px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 30px;
  }

  .phone-mock {
    margin-top: 44px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 340px;
    border-radius: 32px;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .phone-mock-header {
    padding: 18px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .phone-avatar {
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .phone-mock-header .name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; text-align: left; }
  .phone-mock-header .status { font-size: 12px; color: var(--green); font-weight: 600; text-align: left; }
  .phone-mock-body { padding: 20px; text-align: left; }

  .chat-bubble {
    background: var(--card-2);
    border-radius: 4px 16px 16px 16px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    max-width: 88%;
  }
  .chat-bubble-user {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
    border-radius: 16px 4px 16px 16px;
    margin-left: auto;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .macro-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .macro-chip {
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-align: center;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 60px;
  }

  .meal-card-mock {
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--card-2);
  }
  .meal-card-mock .img {
    height: 130px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,99,255,0.35), rgba(0,212,164,0.15));
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 50px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .meal-card-mock .tag {
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px; left: 12px;
    background: var(--accent);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .meal-card-mock .info { padding: 16px; }
  .meal-card-mock .info h4 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .meal-card-mock .info p { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 12px; }

  .mode-pills {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .mode-pill {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 9px 0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .mode-pill.active { background: var(--accent); color: white; }

  .workout-pill-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 16px; }
  .workout-pill {
    padding: 9px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .workout-pill.selected { background: var(--orange); border-color: var(--orange); color: white; }

  /* ---------- WHY BETA ---------- */
  .why-beta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .perks {
    margin-top: 44px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 480px;
  }
  .perk {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 20px 22px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .perk-num {
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--green));
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 15px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .perk-text strong { display: block; font-size: 15.5px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .perk-text span { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--text-dim); }

  /* ---------- URGENCY ---------- */
  .urgency {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .spots-card {
    margin-top: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(108,99,255,0.15), rgba(255,77,109,0.08));
    border: 1px solid rgba(108,99,255,0.4);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 460px;
  }
  .spots-number {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-light), var(--red));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }
  .spots-label {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .spots-bar {
    margin-top: 24px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .spots-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    width: 22%;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--red));
  }
  .spots-sub {
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ---------- FINAL CTA ---------- */
  .final-cta {
    min-height: 92vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .final-cta h2 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 44px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    max-width: 540px;
  }
  .final-cta .sub {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 420px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .cta-primary.big {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 24px 48px;
    font-size: 21px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .socials {
    margin-top: 52px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .social-pill {
    padding: 12px 22px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--card);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  footer {
    padding: 50px 28px 70px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 600;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  footer .heart { color: var(--red); }

  @media (max-width: 380px) {
    h1 { font-size: 44px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 30px; }
    .final-cta h2 { font-size: 34px; }
    .spots-number { font-size: 58px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="viewport"><div class="reel" id="reel">

  <div class="glow glow-1"></div>
  <div class="glow glow-2"></div>
  <div class="glow glow-3"></div>
  <div class="glow glow-4"></div>

  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="badge"><span class="dot"></span>Bêta fermée · Places limitées</div>
    <div class="hero-icon">💪</div>
    <h1>Ton coach <span class="accent">IA</span> qui connaît vraiment ta <span class="accent-green">cuisine</span> et ton <span class="accent">salon</span>.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">FitCoachAI génère tes repas et tes séances maison en quelques secondes — et s'adapte à toi, pas l'inverse.</p>
    <a href="https://tally.so/r/Bzgare" class="cta-primary">Rejoindre la bêta <span class="cta-arrow">→</span></a>
    <p class="cta-note">Gratuit pendant la bêta · <span class="green-text">aucune CB demandée</span></p>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ PROBLEM ============ -->
  <section class="problem">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Le constat</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Manger sain et bouger,<br>ça finit toujours en charge mentale.</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Entre "qu'est-ce que je mange ce soir", les calculs de macros, et les séances qu'on improvise mal — la motivation part vite.</p>
    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="problem-card"><span class="x">✕</span><p>Toujours les mêmes 5 recettes par manque d'idées</p></div>
      <div class="problem-card"><span class="x">✕</span><p>Pas le temps de calculer calories et protéines</p></div>
      <div class="problem-card"><span class="x">✕</span><p>Aucune salle de sport ou équipement à la maison</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ FEATURE: MAX ============ -->
  <section class="feature">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Fonctionnalité 01</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Max, ton coach qui répond <span class="accent">en vrai</span>.</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Dis-lui ce que tu manges, comment tu te sens, ou demande une séance — il note tout et s'adapte à ton objectif.</p>
    <div class="phone-mock">
      <div class="phone-mock-header">
        <div class="phone-avatar" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--green))">🤖</div>
        <div>
          <div class="name">Max</div>
          <div class="status">Coach IA · En ligne</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="phone-mock-body">
        <div class="chat-bubble">Dis-moi ce que t'as mangé, comment tu te sens, ou demande-moi une séance maison 💪</div>
        <div class="chat-bubble chat-bubble-user">Bu 2 cafés ce matin</div>
        <div class="chat-bubble">✅ Noté ! <strong>Café (2 tasses)</strong> — 10 kcal
          <div class="macro-row">
            <div class="macro-chip">🥩 0g</div>
            <div class="macro-chip">🍞 2g</div>
            <div class="macro-chip">🧈 0g</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ FEATURE: PLATS ============ -->
  <section class="feature">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Fonctionnalité 02</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">3 façons de manger <span class="accent-green">sans réfléchir</span>.</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Des idées tendance, des classiques simples à faire ce soir, ou des recettes avec ce qu'il y a déjà dans ton frigo.</p>
    <div class="phone-mock">
      <div class="phone-mock-body" style="padding-top:24px">
        <div class="mode-pills">
          <div class="mode-pill active">✨ Tendance</div>
          <div class="mode-pill">🥗 Simple</div>
          <div class="mode-pill">🧊 Mon frigo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="meal-card-mock">
          <div class="img"><span class="tag">Petit-déj</span>🍳</div>
          <div class="info">
            <h4>Omelette moelleuse au chèvre</h4>
            <p>Garnie de fromage de chèvre fondant et ciboulette fraîche</p>
            <div class="macro-row">
              <div class="macro-chip">🥩 28g</div>
              <div class="macro-chip">🍞 8g</div>
              <div class="macro-chip">🧈 30g</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ FEATURE: BOUGE ============ -->
  <section class="feature">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Fonctionnalité 03</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Une séance <span class="accent">maison</span>, sur-mesure, en 10 secondes.</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Humeur, temps dispo, objectif — l'IA construit une séance adaptée à ce que tu as vraiment envie de faire aujourd'hui.</p>
    <div class="phone-mock">
      <div class="phone-mock-body" style="padding-top:24px">
        <p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:10px;text-align:left">⏱ Temps dispo</p>
        <div class="workout-pill-row">
          <div class="workout-pill">10 min</div>
          <div class="workout-pill selected">20 min</div>
          <div class="workout-pill">30 min</div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-dim);margin:18px 0 10px;text-align:left">🎯 Objectif</p>
        <div class="workout-pill-row">
          <div class="workout-pill selected">Brûler des cal</div>
          <div class="workout-pill">Prendre du muscle</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ WHY JOIN BETA ============ -->
  <section class="why-beta">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Pourquoi rejoindre maintenant</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Les bêta-testeurs façonnent <span class="accent">vraiment</span> l'app.</h2>
    <div class="perks">
      <div class="perk">
        <div class="perk-num">1</div>
        <div class="perk-text"><strong>Accès gratuit total</strong><span>Toutes les fonctionnalités premium débloquées pendant la bêta</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="perk">
        <div class="perk-num">2</div>
        <div class="perk-text"><strong>Ton avis change l'app</strong><span>Chaque retour est lu et beaucoup sont intégrés sous 48h</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="perk">
        <div class="perk-num">3</div>
        <div class="perk-text"><strong>Avantage early adopter</strong><span>Les premiers testeurs gardent des bénéfices au lancement public</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ URGENCY ============ -->
  <section class="urgency">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Places limitées</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">On garde la bêta <span class="accent">petite</span>, exprès.</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Moins de testeurs = plus d'attention sur chaque retour. Une fois les places prises, il faudra attendre le lancement public.</p>
    <div class="spots-card">
      <div class="spots-number">12</div>
      <div class="spots-label">Places restantes</div>
      <div class="spots-bar"><div class="spots-bar-fill"></div></div>
      <p class="spots-sub">Les invitations partent par ordre d'inscription</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ FINAL CTA ============ -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="hero-icon">🚀</div>
    <h2>Prêt à tester FitCoachAI avant tout le monde ?</h2>
    <p class="sub">2 minutes pour t'inscrire. On t'envoie ton accès dès qu'une place se libère.</p>
    <a href="https://tally.so/r/Bzgare" class="cta-primary big">Je rejoins la bêta <span class="cta-arrow">→</span></a>
